{
  "stem": "27150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, the second trip was stopped because it was the 10th of November, I remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a fellow on a bike stopped the [INAUDIBLE] truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, and he said, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews run away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because tomorrow is the 11th of November, and they already-- the German already took a group of people and executed it on the marketplace or something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we approached another smuggler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this time, we went to a place called Mordy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "M-O-R-D-Y.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went over there, I remember, you see, we were there in a sort of back yard of a house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember my mother came and-- and brought some cheesecakes that smelt that [? oil, ?] you see, she-- she dressed with a [? sheet ?] hung over her head like a shiksa, you see, like a peasant.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And gave us a cake, and we went-- and we came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was sort of a nightfall because it was already the 13th of-- almost-- of November.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came to an inn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from that there were a few people who put us in a van, maybe 20 people from different buses on a big fisherman's boat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we crossed a river.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bug, B-U-G, which was the border between, I think the Russian zone and the German zone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they left us on the bank, on the other bank, on the Russian bank.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we paid a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
